FURTHER INVESTIGATION IS DEMANDED TO REASSESS THE STRUCTURAL INTEGRITY OF THE BUILDING BY A TEAM OF STRUCTURAL EXPERTS, AND FOR THE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH TO CERTIFY IF THE CENTRAL BLOCK BUILDING IS STILL VIABLE FOR HOSPITAL USE</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>TEVES, ARNOLFO JR. A.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-01-29</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON HEALTH ON 2018-02-13</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PREVIOUS COMMITTEE REFERRALS :PRIMARILY REFERRED TO RULES on 2018-01-31;</td></tr></table>